on the planet like them.

00:56.934 --> 00:58.925
This thought motivates them
to get out of bed,

00:59.102 --> 01:01.514
eat food, and walk around
like nothing's wrong.

01:01.688 --> 01:04.179
My name is Oliver Tate.

01:06.777 --> 01:08.859
♪ ALEX TURNER: Stuck On The Puzzle

