how people would react to my death.

02:35.157 --> 02:39.116
Mr Dunthorne's quavering voice
as he makes the announcement.

02:40.120 --> 02:42.782
The shocked faces of my classmates.

02:44.374 --> 02:47.241
A playground bedecked with flowers.

02:48.253 --> 02:51.120
